text.tspan: AutoValves connected to GIL are controlled by the
ManualValves connected to GIL are manually
InertOperate GIL inert valve (V29) and GIL
ActivateWill open GIL valve (V28) in both Pacs
CloseWill close GIL valve (V28) in both Pacs
Emergency StopWill shut down BC, MGE, EL and Storage
Note! It’s not possible to activate GIL if both engine lines (EL) are active. This may cause a change over to DO/HFOfor the DGs,fed from
the LNG Pac that is going to be closeddown. Both EL and MGE have to be Closed before GIL activation is enabled.
